{"tid":2347568,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"律師會理事轟官媒施壓終院","createTime":"2020-12-31T06:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T07:36:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b442d06bce9a90e238cc06d185f334cf844f7d59","tid":2347568,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:55:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/H3JNY6FIQZCLPHSQ7MW7ZJKNJM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FH3JNY6FIQZCLPHSQ7MW7ZJKNJM%2F&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm3wORrEXjPgA%2FW0mwV49OOk%3D&h=99ad6cf2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FH3JNY6FIQZCLPHSQ7MW7ZJKNJM%2F&h=d8d29e4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/H3JNY6FIQZCLPHSQ7MW7ZJKNJM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n律師會理事轟官媒施壓終院<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DrprnwwfGYfFRJtN_OS69ok-f-U=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PORDHIO4UVBCVL3FPDYZ2OWYP4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDrprnwwfGYfFRJtN_OS69ok-f-U%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPORDHIO4UVBCVL3FPDYZ2OWYP4.jpg&h=04df2b81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■五名律師會理事發聯署聲明批評《人民日報》向法院施壓。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】終審法院今日將處理律政司就壹傳媒創辦人黎智英獲准保釋提出的上訴，中共官媒《人民日報》及左報連日無視香港司法獨立發文攻擊法院，企圖向終院施壓。繼大律師公會後，律師會五名理事以個人名義發聲明，批評。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警守黎智英寓所查進出者<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n促律政司採行動<br />\n<br />\n「人權律師」帝理邁（Daly Mark Douglas）、林洋鋐、彭皓昕、蔡頴德和黃耀初五名律師會理事以個人名義發表聯署聲明，批評中共官媒《人民日報》攻擊法院批准黎智英保釋，更聲稱有足夠證據顯示黎觸犯國安法第55條，可移交大陸審訊。聲明認為，由國家政權控制和營運報章刊登有關評論文章，「令人尤其擔心及被視為是試圖干預我們獨立的司法機關的程序公義」。<br />\n<br />\n聲明又指，公眾有權根據事實及法律討論法院裁決，惟不應流於政治抹黑，或企圖向法院就某些案件裁決施壓，否則勢對司法機構聲譽、專業和獨立造成嚴重破壞，「特別是《人民日報》刊登的評論文章，會被視為明顯地向法院將要審理的案件施加壓力，此舉可以是違反審理中的案件不應評論的原則，以及有損公平審訊。這些攻擊應當立即停止」。<br />\n<br />\n聲明呼籲律政司採取行動，維護司法機構免受官方控制或營運媒體的不實指控，強調港府有法律責任保護港人的各種基本權利，包括獲得公平審訊的權利。<br />\n<br />\n律政司回覆查詢時未有評論《大公報》和《人民日報》報道和評論是否已構成向司法機構施壓，只。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/go1E4tyh4x0AGnWYApLgjElvDXw=/591x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KW4I7QZHCJERHCWG6VJ25ORKKY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fgo1E4tyh4x0AGnWYApLgjElvDXw%3D%2F591x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKW4I7QZHCJERHCWG6VJ25ORKKY.jpg&h=d9b38d8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n帝理邁"},{"pid":"8c2c5fc5ee6669e86395963c0caaec3812fe7dd9","tid":2347568,"uid":284432,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:22:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f96b112fe64bc6527b64f8426bbd529f98fd1bd3","tid":2347568,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:25:22.000Z","msg":"港式司法獨立：<br />\n<br />\n官媒咪出聲 比我獨立地迫害香港人"},{"pid":"81b5637dd08323e594fc9d451e98ca2dbc76ce5e","tid":2347568,"uid":237914,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:26:19.000Z","msg":"中間條女幾仁"},{"pid":"405a7d1d489518f258e318a4ab7c17cb5e582878","tid":2347568,"uid":282347,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:36:59.000Z","msg":"帝理邁譯得好有霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}